        {
          "title": "Rashi holds nitzok is chibur for yayin nesech; Rabbeinu Tam disagrees",
          "display_title": "Rashi vs. Rabbeinu Tam",
          "timestamp": "54:15"
        },
        {
          "title": "Tosafot: if large loss (hefsed merubeh), rely on Rabbeinu Tam's leniency",
          "display_title": "Hefsed Merubeh Leniency",
